36 Āsavavippayuttasāsavaduka, Kusalattika
Āsavavippayuttasāsavaduka, Kusalattika
45.
132Āsavavippayuttaṃ sāsavaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavavippayutto naanāsavo nakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā…  ekaṃ.
133Āsavavippayuttaṃ anāsavaṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavavippayutto naanāsavo nakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā…  ekaṃ. Hetuyā dve…pe…  avigate dve.
134Āsavavippayuttaṃ sāsavaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca āsavavippayutto naanāsavo naakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Hetuyā ekaṃ…pe…  avigate ekaṃ.
135Āsavavippayuttaṃ sāsavaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paccayā āsavavippayutto nasāsavo naabyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Āsavavippayuttaṃ sāsavaṃ abyākataṃ dhammaṃ paccayā āsavavippayutto naanāsavo naabyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… . Hetuyā dve…pe…  avigate dve.
136Āsavagocchakaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.
